\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 What does health insurance cover?\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Health insurance covers treatment for acute conditions that start after your policy begins.\cb1 \
\cb3 An acute condition is:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 an illness or injury that is likely to respond to treatment,\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 something that you can recover from.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Health insurance doesn\'92t cover:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 conditions that you had before your policy started,\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 ongoing conditions for which there isn\'92t a known cure, like arthritis or diabetes.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Although, long-term treatment for cancer or mental health conditions may be covered even if the condition can\'92t be cured.\cb1 \
\cb3 The level of cover you\'92ll get depends on your policy.\cb1 \
\cb3 Some policies cover treatment and diagnosis. This means that any appointments or tests needed to find out what\'92s wrong could be had privately.\cb1 \
\cb3 Some policies only cover treatment. This means that you\'92d get a diagnosis from the NHS. You\'92d then ask for a referral for private treatment.\cb1 \
\cb3 For more about what is and isn\'92t covered, visit our\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bupa.co.uk/health/health-insurance/compare-cover-options"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 compare cover\'a0}}page.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \strokec4 Which Bupa health insurance option is right for me?\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 We have two levels of health insurance cover.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Comprehensive health insurance\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 This covers medical costs from diagnosis to treatment. If you\'92d like private consultations and tests to find out what\'92s wrong, as well as private treatment, this policy might be best for you.\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Treatment and Care health insurance\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 If you\'92re happy to be diagnosed by the NHS, but want to receive private treatment, this policy might work for you. It\'92s cheaper than our Comprehensive policy as it just covers treatment after you\'92ve been diagnosed.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 You can also include cancer cover as part of our Comprehensive or Treatment and Care policies. There are two levels of cancer cover to choose from.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Full cancer cover.\'a0This covers you from private diagnosis to treatment and aftercare.\cb1 \
\ls4\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 NHS Cancer Cover Plus.\'a0This is cheaper, and just allows you to access private treatment for cancer if the NHS are unable to provide the treatment you need. Specifically, you\'92ll be covered for private chemotherapy, radiotherapy, drug therapy or operations.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 For full details about our cancer cover, see our\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bupa.co.uk/health/health-insurance/bupa-cancer-promise"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \cb3 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 cancer promise}}\'a0page.\cb1 \
\cb3 You can get a quote online now. Or get in touch and we\'92ll talk you through your options. Call our team on 0808 115 3461. Lines are open Monday to Friday 8am to 8pm and Saturday 9am to 12.30pm.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Why should I compare health insurance?\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 It can be tricky to know what to look out for when you\'92re choosing health insurance. The level of care you need will depend on your lifestyle and the aspects of health you\'92re most concerned about. You\'92ll also need to consider your budget.\cb1 \
\cb3 That\'92s why comparing different health insurance policies can be useful. By getting quotes for different levels of cover you\'92ll be able to compare the costs against the benefits. This will help you make an informed decision.\cb1 \
\cb3 When considering your options, you might want to look for a package that covers the following:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Hospital treatment\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Out-patient therapies\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Aftercare\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 		\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Tests and scans\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Make sure you fully understand a health insurance policy before joining. You\'92ll need to know what it includes and excludes to be certain it meets your needs. Most health insurers also offer discounts for\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bupa.co.uk/health/health-insurance/couple-health-insurance"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \cb3 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 couples}}\'a0and\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bupa.co.uk/health/health-insurance/family-health-insurance"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \cb3 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 families}}.\cb1 \
\cb3 You can view a comparison table on our\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bupa.co.uk/health/health-insurance/compare-cover-options"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 compare cover}}\'a0page.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec3 Leaving your company health\uc0\u8232 insurance scheme?\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 Want to keep your cover after leaving your job? Call us on\'a00808 250 1900.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Continue your health insurance cover after leaving your job\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 If you\'92re leaving your employer, you can keep your health insurance going by starting a new, personal policy with us.\cb1 \
\cb3 Your new policy will be different from your employee cover. But you may be able to continue with your treatments. And we may continue to cover any ongoing conditions you have.\cb1 \
\cb3 To get continuous cover, you\'92ll need to start your new policy within three months of your old cover ending.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
