\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Give us a call and keep your cover in 3 easy steps:\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 Step 1.\'a0Call us on 0808 250 1900\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 Call us within 3 months of your scheme ending. We can backdate your new policy to the date you left.\
Lines are open Monday to Friday 8am to 8pm.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \strokec6 Step 2.\'a0\cf2 \cb7 \strokec2 Quick questions\cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 We\'92ll ask you a few questions about your medical history in the last 5 years to give you a new quote.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \strokec6 Step 3.\'a0\cf2 \cb7 \strokec2 Start your policy\cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 Start your policy by paying from the date your old policy ended, so there\'92s no break in your cover.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb8 \strokec2 Our health insurance benefits\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Bupa private medical insurance is designed to suit your health and wellbeing needs. You can expect all of this and more:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Come to us direct, without waiting to see a GP\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 If you\'92re worried about cancer, mental health or muscles, bones and joints, you can call our Direct Access team. We\'92ll check that your symptoms are covered and give you clear advice on what to do next. We could refer you to a specialist on the call. Or, if you do need to see a GP, we\'92ll let you know.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 See a GP without going anywhere\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Most Bupa cover includes Bupa Blua Health, or another digital GP service\'87. This means you can talk to a GP within 24 hours \'96 day or night. Book a video or phone call from home, work or wherever. And if you\'92re happy to pay for a private prescription, you can pay to have it delivered to your door.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Whatever the mental health condition, we\'92ll be there.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Your emotional wellbeing is as important as your physical health. That\'92s why we cover more mental health conditions than any other leading UK insurer.\cf2 \cb3 \super \strokec2 \'86\cf2 \cb3 \nosupersub \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Nurses ready to help, every hour of the day\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Late at night or first thing in the morning, our Anytime HealthLine connects you to a qualified nurse when you have a health concern. Clear and simple advice from someone who cares.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Access to breakthrough cancer drugs\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Our cancer cover can offer some cancer drugs and treatments before they\'92re available on the NHS. Helping you get the medicines you need, faster. Any drugs or treatments will need to be evidence-based and covered by your policy.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Rewards from brands you know and love\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Fitness, nutrition, relaxation, getting outdoors. Whatever works for you or your partner\'92s wellbeing, we want to save you money on it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 Make the most of your Bupa health insurance\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 From making a claim or checking your account, to getting an appointment, all the help you need is right here.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 How can I make a claim?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 If you need treatment and would like to make a claim, you\'92ll usually need to have visited your GP and received a referral. In some cases, you can submit a claim without a GP referral.\cb1 \
\cb3 If your cover includes\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bupa.co.uk/health/health-insurance/speak-to-a-specialist"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \cb3 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 Direct Access}}, you can speak to us about some symptoms as soon as you\'92re worried. You may even be able to get treatment without seeing a GP.\cb1 \
\cb3 When claiming, you\'92ll need your Bupa membership number as well as details about your diagnosis and treatment.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec3 Guide to making a health insurance claim\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb8 \strokec6 Do your symptoms fall into any of these categories?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \cb1 \outl0\strokewidth0 - Cancer Symptoms \
- Muscles, Bones and Joints\
- Mental Health\
- Moles and skin cancer concerns.\cf6 \cb8 \outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 If you\'92re experiencing any of these symptoms and you have Direct Access, call us directly. We\'92ll check that your symptoms are covered and explain how you can get help. You may be able to get treatment without a GP referral.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 If your symptoms aren\'92t listed above, follow our step by step guide:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Step 1:\cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \uc0\u8232 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 See a GP\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 If your symptoms aren\'92t covered by our Direct Access service, you should speak to a GP first.\
Book an appointment with your own GP or through a digital GP service. They can advise you if you need to see a specialist or healthcare professional..\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Speak to a GP within 24 hours from anywhere\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 With our digital GP services, you can get professional advice at a time that suits you. .\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Health advice day or night\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 With our Anytime HealthLine, you can get health advice from a nurse at any time of the night or day..\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \strokec4 Step 2:\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Ask the GP for an open referral\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 If you have a condition that requires a GP referral, we recommend you ask for an \'91Open Referral letter\'92. This will detail the care your GP would like you to have, but will not be addressed to a specific consultant, hospital, or healthcare professional.\
The referral needs to include the type of speciality that you have been referred to.\
We aim to offer a choice of two or three specialists. If the first-choice consultant is unavailable, you can see someone else without having to return to your GP for a second referral.\
You can also choose to speak to a specialist over the phone or by video. You can call us on 0345 609 0111 to discuss your options. Lines are open 8am - 8pm Monday to Friday, 8am-4pm Saturdays.\
Important:\'a0Open Referral is mandatory on some personal, corporate and company schemes. If you need help, please call us on 0345 609 0444. Lines are open Monday to Friday 8am to 8pm and Saturday 9am to 12.30pm.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \strokec4 Step 3:\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Contact us for a pre-authorisation code\cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 As soon as you\'92ve seen your GP please contact us. We\'92ll discuss your options and explain what you\'92re covered for. Our advisor will talk you through what you need to do next and will send any pre-treatment forms that you need to complete.\
If you\'92re covered we will give you a pre-authorisation code. You\'92ll show this to your specialist. It lets them know that Bupa has approved your treatment.\
Here's what you'll need when you contact us:\
