\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 What happens next?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 See your pre-authorisation in Bupa Touch\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa300\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 If you've been referred to see a healthcare specialist, it\'92s important to talk to us so we can check that your treatment is covered. Once we have established that it is, we'll give you a pre-authorisation code.\
